spec_name: cns-prng-params
spec_role: SV7/SV8 case -1 noise-substitution PRNG scalar parameters (two-LFSR generator + per-sample mapping)
c_identifier: (literals in mpc_random_int / mpc_decoder reset + Q-decode)
c_type: mixed (int seeds / hex tap masks / shift / bias)
raw_dims: [6][2]
resolved_dims: [6][2]
element_count: 6
columns: parameter,value
value_encoding: see per-row; masks in hex, others decimal
source_file: libmpcdec/synth_filter.c + libmpcdec/mpc_decoder.c
source_sha256: f5a4aa9ebe291be5cb28f1ff5644e477066a0650c9d0b3de004fcbe76d189541
repo_url: https://github.com/tatsuz/musepack
repo_commit: 15feced545c3fce808b00b184b2361d53825e159
extractor: extract.py (pure numeric extraction)
notes: r1=(r1>>1)|(Parity[r1&0xF5]<<31); r2=(r2<<1)|Parity[(r2>>25)&0x63]; word=r1^r2; noise q = (b0+b1+b2+b3) - 510 over the 4 bytes of word. Seeds set to 1 at decoder reset.
